  15,6,"Nnan: \"a win u$uĂŽ d irs usmekti! KeĂ§Ă§, war ccekk, d aĂŽehbani"
  15,7,"Acimi ur a$ d tusiv ara, s lmalayek, ma d tidep ay tessawalev"
  15,8,"Ur Nesrusu lmalayek, siwa s tidep. Imiren, ur pganin"
  15,9,"Ih, Nekwni Nessers ed asmekti. Ih, Nekwni a NĂȘareb fellas"
