  15,22,"Nuzen ed avu isswayen. Nesse$li d aman seg igenni, yissen Nessew ikwen. Ur llin ara lexzayen is $uĂŽwen"
  15,23,"Ih, d Nekwni i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. D Nekwni ay d IweĂŽĂŽaten"
  15,24,"Ni$ Nessen imezwura nnwen, Nessen ineggura"
  15,25,"Ih, Mass ik, Neppa, a ten id Ifser. Ih, Neppa, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab, d Amusnaw"
  15,26,Ni$ Nexleq amdan si talaxt taberkant i meslen
  15,27,"Nexleq loenn, iu$ lĂȘal, si tmes n ccili"
